        <item>
            <title>Version 1.0.0</title>
            <sparkle:version>1.0.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>10.0.17763</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 16:22:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Remio Client for Windows 1.0.0</h2>
                <p>First public release of the native Windows client.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Native WinUI 3 experience with Mica backdrop and dark/light theme</li>
                    <li>Hardware-accelerated H.264/H.265 decoding (D3D11VA + FFmpeg)</li>
                    <li>Full input parity with iOS/Android: keyboard, mouse, scroll, gamepad, clipboard sync</li>
                    <li>Adaptive WebRTC streaming with automatic relay/direct path negotiation</li>
                    <li>Per-user installation &mdash; no admin/UAC required</li>
                    <li>Built-in auto-update via WinSparkle (EdDSA-signed)</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
